      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver verified against at least one canonical benchmark with known analytical solution.",
      "rationale": "Fluent verified against the Hagen-Poiseuille analytical solution for laminar pipe flow and against the Taylor-Green vortex for turbulent dissipation. Both benchmarks pass within solver-published tolerances."
