      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoI directly maps to the clinical endpoint (hemolysis) used in the regulatory submission.",
      "rationale": "NIH and relative hemolysis index RH are the quantities computed. RH is the acceptance criterion in the 510(k) comparison against the predicate device. Direct traceability to clinical hemolysis endpoint confirmed."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
