      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation geometry, fluid, and operating envelope match or bound the COU device and intended operating range.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry, which is the same platform used in the COU. Operating points span 2–6 L/min and 2000–4000 rpm, encompassing the CPB clinical envelope. Fluid is bovine blood surrogate at matched hematocrit."
    },
