      "rationale": "At MRL 2 a formal model-form uncertainty quantification is not required. The k-omega SST turbulence model with Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis power-law is standard practice for centrifugal blood pump CFD and is accepted by FDA guidance. No further assessment conducted."
    },
